        {
          "anchor": "return-value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A new rendering context. The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "aglCreateContext",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " function returns ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "NULL",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " if the function fails for any reason. You can call the function ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.agl/documentation/AGL/aglGetError",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to determine what the error is.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If the pixel format object you supply is able to support multiple graphics devices, then the rendering context can render transparently across the supported devices. With a multiple-device rendering context, sharing is possible only when the relationship between the renderers and the graphics devices they support is the same for all rendering contexts that are shared. Normally you achieve the best results by using the same pixel format object for all shared rendering contexts. For more information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/GraphicsImaging/Conceptual/OpenGL-MacProgGuide/opengl_intro/opengl_intro.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40001987",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
